    git-turnouts config check --optional   # Only optional tools

REQUIRED TOOLS:
    git          Version control and worktree management (requires 2.5+)
    bash         Script execution (requires 3.2+)
    jq           JSON parsing for GitHub PR integration

OPTIONAL TOOLS:
